rows.name: Otto went to the Nocclia Timber Site.

rows.label: qst200919_msg0002
rows.name:
Something might've happened to
him on the road.

rows.label: qst200919_msg0003
rows.name:
Could you head up to the Nocclia
Timber Site and keep an eye out
for him on your way there?

I'm sure you lot'll be fine out there,
but worst comes to worst, you save
your own skins,okay?
